none: media/user/SCRAPE/test/2016-09-monkey-brain/extracted/Monkey Brain/04 Searching For A Better Choice

Originally ripped by Terminal Escape, posted on September 30, 2016 Description from Terminal Escape:
Undoubtedly dated catchy punk from Curitiba. Delivery is splotchy at times, and the combination of East Bay pop and US DIY melodic "hardcore" (that's what we called it then, kids) is likely to send anyone under 35 running....but fukk it. "Searching For A Better Choice" is still a banger, and I'll even take the damned ska track(s). So there.  WAKE UP TIME!!
